<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN303-intro">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. erumai veḷiyaṉār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN303">
<l>nilampiṟak kiṭuvatu pōṟkuḷampu kaṭaiyūu</l>
<l>vuḷḷa moḻikkuṅ koṭpiṉ māṉmē</l>
<l>leḷḷunarc cekukkuṅ kāḷai kūrtta</l>
<l>ventiṟa leḵka neñcuvaṭu viḷaippa</l>
<l>vāṭṭik kāṇiya varumē nerunai</l>
<l>yuraicāl ciṟappiṉ vēntar muṉṉark</l>
<l>karaiporu munnīrt tiraiyiṟ pōḻntavar</l>
<l>kayantalai maṭappiṭi pulampa</l>
<l>vilaṅkumarup piyāṉai yeṟinta veṟkē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="3a-c">The young man who destroys those who deride [him], </l>
<l corresp="2">upon a restless horse that finishes off the mind </l>
<l corresp="1">by pressing down [its] hooves as if putting behind the ground, </l>
<l>with [his] sharp cruel powerful blade he made [them] fade </l>
<l corresp="4-5c">when [their] hearts were exhausted by [their] injuries, [and] comes in order to see </l>
<l>me who yesterday had attacked an elephant with shining tusks (5d+9)</l>
<l corresp="8">so that [its] soft-headed youthful elephant cow would be lonely, </l>
<l corresp="6a-c">[the elephant] of the kings with praise-worthy excellence </l>
<l corresp="6d-7">who had previously cut into [our front numerous] like the waves of the sea that beats against the shore. </l>
</lg>
    </div>
